results.title: Does azure support Themify Builder plugin on wordpress? - Microsoft Q&A
results.description: | Yes, the Themify Builder plugin is compatible with WordPress installations on Microsoft Azure. Themify Builder is a versatile drag-and-drop page builder that works with any WordPress theme. It is compatible with major plugins like WooCommerce, Yoast SEO, WPML, and Contact Form 7, and supports custom post types, shortcodes, and HTML tags. To.
